\par His back was to Llewellyn, who saw only the powerful line of shoulders outlined beneath the thin yellow shirt and a broad-brimmed battered felt hat stuck on the back of the painter}{\insrsid5328970 \rquote }{\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5328970 
